data.oai_dc:dc: Canopy Hieght Data from Barro Colorado Island 50 Hectare Plot
The canopy height at every 5 meters in the Barro Colorado Island 50 hectare plot is measured with a rangefinder in the years 1993, 1995, 1996, 2000, 2001, 2003, 2004, and 2005.
